Researched WebSocket reconnection best practices. Key findings: (1) Native WebSocket lacks reconnection - must implement, (2) Exponential backoff + jitter is industry standard (min=1s, max=20s, factor=1.3), (3) reconnecting-websocket library (1.5M downloads/week) recommended for lobs-server. Delivered comprehensive 31KB guide with production patterns, comparison of strategies, implementation roadmap, and testing recommendations. Recommended: Use reconnecting-websocket wrapper as Phase 1 quick win (1-2 hours implementation).